title: Townhome for rent from August 15
posting_body: Beautiful town-home, 2 bedrooms and 2.5 baths at Sammamish Hills.
Open living & dining rooms accented by built in cabinets and a wood burning Fireplace.
First floor gleams with Cherry hardwood and kitchen shines with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances.
A spacious master with an on-suite bath allows privacy and the & 3 closets gets you plenty of storage.
Second bedroom is also large w/ample closets.
Second floor is complete with the laundry units.
Two car tandem garage and a great location just off I-90 that gets you an easy commute to Seattle & Bellevue.
